skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: spark support
des:
Hey, friend. We are Spark. 
We're a mental health charity, and we've developed our very first Alexa skill to try and help you through days when you might not be feeling at your best. 
Ask us for something to help you through, and we'll do our best to help!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
